<p rend="chapter">Ganthārambhakathā</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="1"><hi rend="paranum">1</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Namassitvā <pb ed="M" n="0.0001" /><pb ed="V" n="0.0001" /> tilokaggaṃ, ñeyyasāgarapāraguṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Bhavābhāvakaraṃ dhammaṃ, gaṇañca guṇasāgaraṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="2"><hi rend="paranum">2</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Nissāya pubbācariyamataṃ atthāvirodhinaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Vakkhāmi saccasaṅkhepaṃ, hitaṃ kārakayoginaṃ.</p>
